OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAfghanistan: Taliban unveil
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fnew rules banning women in 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FTV dramas                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Women have been banned from appearing  
OL,6, in television dramas in Afghanistan    
OL,7, under new rules imposed by the Taliban 
OL,8, government.                            
OL,10,FFemale journalists and presenters have 
OL,11,Falso been ordered to wear headscarves  
OL,12,Fon screen, although the guidelines do  
OL,13,Fnot say which type of covering to use. 
OL,15,FReporters say some of the rules are    
OL,16,Fvague and subject to interpretation.   
OL,18,FThe Taliban seized power in Afghanistan
OL,19,Fin mid-August and many fear they are   
OL,20,Fgradually imposing harsh restrictions. 
